text: Kyzyl-Oktyabr may refer to the following places in Kyrgyzstan: *Kyzyl-Oktyabr, Chuy, a village in Kemin District, Chuy Region *Kyzyl-Oktyabr, Jalal-Abad, a village in Bazar-Korgon District, Jalal-Abad Region *Kyzyl-Oktyabr, Uzgen, a village in Uzgen District, Osh Region *Kyzyl-Oktyabr, Talas, a village in Bakay-Ata District, Talas Region
title: Kyzyl-Oktyabr
